<h2 id='view-switcher'>View Switcher</h2>
<p>Searchkit&#39;s view switcher components come in 2 seperate components. <code>ViewSwitcherHits</code> which toggles the hits display and <code>ViewSwitcherToggle</code> which is the actual toggle button to switch views.</p>

<p><img src="./assets/view-switch-grid.png" height="200px"/>
<img src="./assets/view-switch-list.png" height="200px"/>
<img src="./assets/view-switch-table.png" height="200px"/></p>
